<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٣٦٠٠ - غ ل ق]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>غلِقَ٢ يغلَق، غَلَقًا وغُلُوقًا، فهو غَلِق<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• غلِق الرّجُلُ:</span> ضاق صدرُه وقلّ صبرُه <span class="c1">"إيّاك والغَلَق والضجر"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>